    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Zenk has a muscular cyan body and a cubic structure in place of a head.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 172     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++      </lightgrey>                \n<darkgrey>    rF: ...     </darkgrey><darkgrey>   rC: ...      </darkgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: ∞        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 180% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 72% to hit with your +7 vampiric lajatang and 68% to hit with your bite, pseudopods, slice, and slice.\nIt has about 31% to hit you.\n\nAttack               Max Damage      \nHit: electric touch  44 + 20 (elec)  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
